com.gembox.spreadsheet.tables

Class TableRowCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gembox.spreadsheet.tables.TableRowCollection

  • public final class TableRowCollection
extends Object
    Represents a collection of Table rows, not including header and, if enabled, totals row. Supported in XLSX only.
